  "prompt": "What do Indian IT companies like Infosys and Tech Mahindra do?",
  "response": "Indian IT companies like Infosys and Tech Mahindra are major players in the global information technology services industry. Here's a brief overview of their core activities:\n\n### Infosys\n1. **Consulting Services**: Infosys provides business consulting services to help organizations improve their efficiency, effectiveness, and profitability.\n2. **Technology Services**: It offers a wide range of technology services including application development and maintenance, infrastructure management, and cloud services.\n3. **Outsourcing**: Infosys helps companies outsource various business processes and IT functions to improve cost efficiency and focus on core business areas.\n4. **Digital Transformation**: The company assists organizations in adopting digital technologies and strategies to transform their business models and operations.\n5. **Engineering Services**: Infosys provides product engineering and lifecycle solutions which include design, development, testing, and maintenance.\n6. **Artificial Intelligence & Automation**: Leveraging AI and automation technologies, Infosys helps clients streamline operations and enhance productivity.\n\n### Tech Mahindra\n1. **IT Services and Solutions**: Tech Mahindra offers services like application development, maintenance, and support, as well as infrastructure management.\n2. **Telecom Solutions**: It provides specialized solutions for the telecommunications sector, including network services and digital transformation.\n3. **Consulting**: Tech Mahindra offers consulting services to help businesses optimize their IT strategies and improve operational efficiency.\n4. **Enterprise Solutions**: The company provides ERP, CRM, and SCM solutions to help businesses manage their operations more effectively.\n5. **Digital Transformation**: Tech Mahindra assists businesses in adopting digital technologies such as cloud computing, IoT, and AI to transform their operations.\n6. **Business Process Outsourcing (BPO)**: It offers BPO services to manage and optimize back-office functions for businesses.\n7. **Cybersecurity**: Tech Mahindra provides cybersecurity solutions to protect businesses from threats and ensure data integrity.\n\nBoth companies have a significant global presence and cater to various industries including finance, healthcare, manufacturing, retail, and more. They are known for their innovation and commitment to delivering high-quality IT solutions and services.",
